These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, mechanic, nurse
1. the mechanic is on the far left##1
2. the videographer is on the right of the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | mechanic | nurse | videographer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, fisherman, social-worker
1. the social-worker is on the far right##1
2. the analyst is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | analyst | fisherman | social-worker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, filmmaking, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | traveling | filmmaking | drawing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: german, thai, italian
1. the thai is on the far right##1
2. the thai is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | german | italian | thai |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, 7up
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | mirinda | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, scooter, motorbike
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | motorbike | scooter | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, sports, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | musical | sports |

 #################################

 
